          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！承嗣首级系在恩人。此番自当知过自新，不复再贻伊戚。所置外宅键儿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "田承嗣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本防他盗，并非异图。今并脱其甲裳，放归田亩，是以小弟特来谢罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛嵩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "区区小事，何足挂齿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "田承嗣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "取盒之人，当是天神下界，不知可允小弟一见否？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛嵩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃小婢所为，何劳奖宠？"
        },
        {
          "character": "田承嗣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦！乃丫鬟所为！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛嵩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田承嗣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "更要相见！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛嵩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我唤她前来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛嵩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "红线进帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "红线进帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（红线上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一夜身经千里路，幸得骊龙项下珠。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（红线进门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公有何吩咐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛嵩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见过田大人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与田大人叩头！"
        },
        {
          "character": "田承嗣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了，罢了！前者进帐取盒，就是你么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田承嗣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀呀！真乃超凡出众！只是那夜床头取盒，路程千里之远，如此迢远，营门"
        },
        {
          "character": "田承嗣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有数重之深，不知你是怎样前去？怎样进帐？可得闻之否？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛嵩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你可讲与大人一听。"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！那夜子时三刻，既达魏城。凡历数门，遂及寝所。观外宅儿止于房廊，"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鼾声雷动；见军中士兵步于庭下，传叫风生。奴婢拨了左扉，直抵绣帐。见大"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人鼓腹酣眠，头枕文犀枕，枕露七星剑。剑前仰开一金盒，内藏生辰八字。时"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "则蜡烛烟微，炉香烬萎，侍人四布，兵仗交罗。或头触屏风，垂头而睡；或手"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "持巾拂，抵足而眠。奴乃拔其簪珥，牵其衣裳，如病如痴，皆不能悟，遂持金"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "盒，御风而归。出魏城西门，将行二百里，见铜台高揭，漳水东流，晨鸡动夜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "斜月在林，好一派宵景也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "田承嗣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此说来，你辛苦了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴婢觉得来回只一刹那耳，又何辛苦之有？只是得罪大人，望乞原宥！"
        },
        {
          "character": "田承嗣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢，岂敢！多谢不杀之恩！"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛嵩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亲翁此话，她哪里受的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "田承嗣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "精妙剑法，可赐一观否？"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何不可。如此，献丑了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "忆从天上谪红尘，"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "游戏人间十六春。"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "略施小伎呈奇能。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（红线舞剑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "望求大人指示分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "田承嗣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙极，妙极！真乃神人也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "红线",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人夸奖了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "田承嗣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊亲家，你帐下有这样的无意剑侠，乃国家之幸也！悔不该当初屡动干戈，承"
        },
        {
          "character": "田承嗣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗣悔之晚矣！今日你我不免两家和好，何怕外寇侵犯西河之岸？天下太平，免"
        },
        {
          "character": "田承嗣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "动刀枪，乃黎民百姓安宁之福也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛嵩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亲翁之言，正合我意，我早已吩咐下去宰猪杀羊，为两家和好与军民共欢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "田承嗣",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，大人请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛嵩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！军士们！痛饮几杯呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛嵩",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈哈……"
        }
      ],
